        <h6 class="mt-5">Prime Ministerâ€™s Citizen Assisstance and Reilief in Emergency Situations Fund <br>
            (PM CARES Fund)</h6>
        <br>
        <p style="font-weight: 400;">Visit the website pmindia.gov.in and donate to the PM CARES Fund using the
            following details : </p>
